#

Filet Mignon with Truffle Mashed Potatoes and Sautéed Asparagus

$75
850 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GourmetSteakComfort Food

Description

A succulent filet mignon paired with creamy truffle mashed potatoes and vibrant sautéed asparagus for a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • Filet Mignon: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Asparagus: 1 pound, trimmed
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Mashed Potatoes: 2 cups
  • Truffle Oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/4 cup, grated
